column5: Wish you the best of good lucks fam

I'm a college student, as if college wasn't an already tortuous experience, I've been feeling like this for a long time, I do have friends, go out to parties and stuff, but everything keeps feeling deeply fake and empty, I can't seem to get along with people anymore without feeling like I'm bothering them in some way, I feel I like if other people feel immediately disgusted towards me all the time and I just can't help it
